full_text: Haley Ramm  is an American actress. She played young Jean Grey in X-Men: The Last Stand and appeared in multiple episodes of the CBS drama Without a Trace throughout 2007 and 2008. Since 2014 Ramm has co-starred in the ABC Family drama Chasing Life.
title: Haley Ramm
